         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:note>The following incipit and explicit, without subscription and supplications, are taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLaethd20"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BDLaethd20</span></t:ref>.</t:note>

            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>ወእንዘ፡ የኃልፍ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ ሀገረ፡ እግዚአብሔር። ርእየ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘዕውሩ፡ ተወልደ፡ እምክርሠ፡ እሙ፡ ዕውር፡ ወበሐም። ወሶበ፡ ሰምዓ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ጸርሐ፡ ወከልሐ፡ በከመ፡ ክሂሎቱ። ወይቤሎ፡ ስምዖን፡ ለእግዚእየ፡ ብፁዕ፡ ዘአእመረ፡ ዘየኃሥሥ፡ ዝዕውር፡ ወበሐም፡ ወይትዌከፍ፡ ቃሎ፡</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>ወሶበ፡ ቀርበ፡ ኀቤሁ፡ አንበረ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ እዴሁ፡ ዲበ፡ አዕይንቲሁ፡ ወርእየ። ወዓዲ፡ አንበረ፡ እምእዘኒሁ፡ ወሰምዓ፡ ሶቤሃ፨ ወአሜሃ፡ ኮነ፡ ፩እምእለ፡ ይስብኩ፡ በስሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ወበእዲሁ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ አምኑ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሕዝብ፡ ወሖሩ፡ ፈለገ፡ ዮርዳኖስ፡  ወተጠምቁ፡ በእደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
         <t:div type="edition">
           <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
             <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/SUPN3FIP"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, II&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1920</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">14/5 (71)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">14/5 (71)</biblScope><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/patrologiaorient14pariuoft</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII</note><t:citedRange unit="page">821</t:citedRange></t:bibl>
             <t:ab>
               እንዘ፡ የኃልፍ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በኢየሩሳሌም፡ ሀገረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ርእየ፡ ብእሴ፡ ዘዕውረ፡ ተወልደ፡ እምከርሠ፡ እሙ፡ ዕውር፡ ወበሀመ፨ ወሶበ፡ ሰምዓ፡ እንዘ፡ የኃልፍ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ጸርኃ፡ ወከልሀ፡ በከመ፡ ክሂሎቱ።
             </t:ab>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
             <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/SUPN3FIP"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, II&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1920</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">14/5 (71)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">14/5 (71)</biblScope><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/patrologiaorient14pariuoft</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1920MiraclesJesusII</note><t:citedRange unit="page">825-826</t:citedRange></t:bibl>
             <t:ab>
               ወአዘዞ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ከመ፡ ይቅረብ፡ ኀቤሁ፡ ወሶበ፡ ቀርበ፡ ኀቤሁ፡ አንበረ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ እዴሁ፡ ዲበ፡ አዕይንቲሁ። ወርእየ፡ ሶቤሃ። ወዓዴ፡ አንበረ፡ ዲበ፡ አእዛኒሁ፡ ወሰምዓ፡ ሶቤሃ። ወእምአሜሃ፡ ኮነ፡ ፩እምእለ፡ ይሰብኩ፡ በስሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ወበእዴሁ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ አምኑ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሕዝብ፡ ወሖሩ፡ ፈለገ፡ ዮርዳኖስ፡ ወተጥመቁ፡ በእደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ።
             </t:ab>
           </t:div>
